<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>If there is more than one instance running in EC2,  Zend_Service_Amazon_Ec2_Instance's describe will only return the last in the reservation set.</p>

<p>This is because onn line 253 the instances array is created and also replaces itself every time a reservation item is looped through.</p>

<p>The reservation id is also replaced since the data structure only allows one.</p>

